OL,3,CGrieving father's film following
OL,4,Cdaughter's murder wins Beverly Hills
OL,5,Caward
OL,7,FTim Edwards and John May spoke to
OL,8,FKatie and Rob about their award-
OL,9,Fwinning documentary which touches on
OL,10,Fmental health and coping with tragedy.
OL,12,FThe father of a woman who was fatally
OL,13,Fshot outside a pub has won an award
OL,14,Ffor his film which documented his
OL,15,Fjourney of dealing with her murder.
OL,17,FElle Edwards, 26, was killed in the
OL,18,Fshooting outside the Lighthouse pub in
OL,19,FWallasey, Wirral, on Christmas Eve
OL,20,F2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
