PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777219865
OL,3,CGrieving father's film following
OL,4,Cdaughter's murder wins Beverly Hills
OL,5,Caward
OL,7,FJust days after the tragedy, her
OL,8,Fgrieving father Tim got in touch with
OL,9,FLiverpool actor John May, who was
OL,10,Fpreparing to walk from Lands End to
OL,11,FJohn O'Groats as part of a campaign to
OL,12,Fend gun and knife crime.
OL,14,FThey released a documentary of their
OL,15,Fjourney, named "The Two of Us" which
OL,16,Fhas now - four years after their
OL,17,Fchallenge - won the award for best
OL,18,Fdocumentary at the 2026 Beverly Hills
OL,19,FFilm Festival.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777219865
OL,3,CGrieving father's film following
OL,4,Cdaughter's murder wins Beverly Hills
OL,5,Caward
OL,7,FJohn May said: "We've also been
OL,8,Fselected for the Melbourne Documentary
OL,9,FFestival in Australia as well, so it's
OL,10,Fjust amazing that this Liverpool story
OL,11,Fwhich spanned the country has
OL,12,Fresonated with people around the world.
OL,14,F"I'm just so proud."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
