OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777219865
OL,3,CGrieving father's film following
OL,4,Cdaughter's murder wins Beverly Hills
OL,5,Caward
OL,7,FMr Edwards took on the walk before the
OL,8,Ftrial of gunman Connor Chapman, who
OL,9,Fwas targeting rivals in a gang feud
OL,10,Fwhen he opened fire outside the pub,
OL,11,Fand was sentenced to a minimum of 48
OL,12,Fyears after being found guilty of Ms
OL,13,FEdwards' murder.
OL,15,FHe said walking with Mr May helped him
OL,16,Fto build a foundation for his future,
OL,17,Fand hoped the documentary would
OL,18,Finspire people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
