CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777219865
OL,3,CGrieving father's film following
OL,4,Cdaughter's murder wins Beverly Hills
OL,5,Caward
OL,7,FTim Edwards said: "It's a bittersweet
OL,8,Fpill, I would swap everything to have
OL,9,Fher here with me now and living that
OL,10,Flife as it was before.
OL,12,F"But that's not going to happen so to
OL,13,Fget something as positive as this out
OL,14,Fof an awful situation, it's the best
OL,15,Fthing that we could do for Ellie and
OL,16,Ffor other people.
OL,18,F"The film's helping people with mental
OL,19,Fhealth issues."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
