OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777219865
OL,3,CGrieving father's film following
OL,4,Cdaughter's murder wins Beverly Hills
OL,5,Caward
OL,7,FThe film, put together from vlogs
OL,8,Ffilmed by the pair at the time and
OL,9,Finterviews once they had returned,
OL,10,Fshows the highs and lows of the
OL,11,Fjourney ` which at one point saw them
OL,12,Fseparating for 10 days after a falling
OL,13,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
